OL,4,Cfuel summer riots, report finds
OL,6,FThe report said: "If there is a thread
OL,7,Fconnecting the high-octane events of
OL,8,Flate July (2024) and the slow local
OL,9,Fpolitics of the pier, it is the loss
OL,10,Fof physical spaces where we might come
OL,11,Ftogether, and the radicalisation of
OL,12,Fsome of the digital spaces that have
OL,13,Freplaced them.
OL,15,F"There is an appetite for community
OL,16,Faction, as the campaign for the pier
OL,17,Fshows, but a lack of investment and
OL,18,Fspace.
