OL,3,CThe closure of community hubs helped
OL,4,Cfuel summer riots, report finds
OL,6,F"In the absence of structures which
OL,7,Fmight foster wider solidarities, many
OL,8,Fretreat into the sphere of the home,
OL,9,For worse, into ethno-nationalist
OL,10,Ffantasies of muscular sovereignty."
OL,12,FReport author Dr Sacha Hilhorst said:
OL,13,F"The Southport riots were a wake-up
OL,14,Fcall ` a stark reminder of what can
OL,15,Fhappen when communities lose the
OL,16,Fplaces that once brought people
OL,17,Ftogether. In the absence of shared
OL,18,Fspaces, misinformation and hate can
OL,19,Ffill the void, creating tinderbox
OL,20,Fconditions for violence.
