OL,6,F"Rebuilding local infrastructure isn't
OL,7,Fjust about nostalgia ` it's a vital
OL,8,Fbulwark against division and the
OL,9,Fdangerous pull of the far right.
OL,11,F"But communities are not apathetic.
OL,12,FThey are crying out for places to
OL,13,Fgather, to organise, and to belong. We
OL,14,Fneed a new generation of institutions
OL,15,Fto help them do just that."
OL,17,FDr Parth Patel, associate director at
OL,18,Fthe IPPR, said: "Where shared spaces
OL,19,Fare lost, a sense of decline and
OL,20,Fdisconnection takes root ` and with
OL,21,Fit, dangerous alternatives thrive.
